WEBVTT

00:10.144 --> 00:12.580
- * ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR,
FIVE, SIX *

00:12.613 --> 00:14.582
* SHAKE IT, DUDE

00:14.615 --> 00:22.556
*

00:35.436 --> 00:38.339
- * CUE THE PULSE TO BEGIN

00:46.347 --> 00:50.284
* CUE THE PULSE TO BEGIN

00:50.318 --> 00:53.487
* CUE THE PULSE TO BEGIN

00:53.521 --> 00:57.325
* CUE THE PULSE TO BEGIN

01:00.394 --> 01:01.429
[ambient music]

01:01.462 --> 01:03.197
- OHH.

01:03.231 --> 01:04.465
- * WOULD YOU LIKE MY

01:04.498 --> 01:08.169
*

01:08.202 --> 01:09.303
- * WOULD YOU LIKE MY

01:09.337 --> 01:13.707
*

01:13.741 --> 01:17.578
- [grunting]

01:17.611 --> 01:21.782
*

01:21.815 --> 01:23.451
- AHH.

01:23.484 --> 01:26.354
- * WOULD YOU LIKE MY,
WOULD YOU LIKE MY *

01:26.387 --> 01:28.456
* WOULD YOU LIKE MY

01:28.489 --> 01:30.724
*

01:30.758 --> 01:34.295
- [grunting]

01:55.249 --> 01:57.385
- SIX DOWN.

01:57.418 --> 01:59.320
VERY IMPRESSIVE.

02:04.325 --> 02:05.826
- SIX AS WELL.

02:05.859 --> 02:07.495
- IT'S A MODEST
EFFORT.

02:07.528 --> 02:09.530
- THIS CAN BE VERIFIED?
- I HAVE SIGNED AFFIDAVITS.

02:09.563 --> 02:12.700
HOW ABOUT YOU?
- THE SAME.

02:12.733 --> 02:14.568
SO IT APPEARS WE'RE
NECK AND NECK.

02:14.602 --> 02:17.405
- DICK AND DICK.
- EQUAL.

02:17.438 --> 02:19.507
- EVEN, BRANDON.

02:19.540 --> 02:22.810
BUT NEVER,
NEVER EQUAL.

02:22.843 --> 02:24.578
- OH, BUT NOT
FOR LONG.

02:24.612 --> 02:27.215
MY NUMBER SEVEN
JUST WALKED IN.

02:28.549 --> 02:31.652
- WHAT DO YOU KNOW?
SO DID MINE.

02:31.685 --> 02:32.653
[chuckles]

02:32.686 --> 02:35.389
AND MY NUMBER EIGHT.

02:35.423 --> 02:36.824
I DON'T BELIEVE THERE WERE
ANY STIPULATIONS

02:36.857 --> 02:39.660
REGARDING MORE THAN ONE
AT A TIME.

02:39.693 --> 02:41.862
[indistinct chatter]

02:45.833 --> 02:47.668
- A COUPLE MORE FEET.

02:47.701 --> 02:49.370
JUST--OHH.

02:50.471 --> 02:51.572
- WHEW!

02:52.840 --> 02:54.708
- THAT WAS A SCHLEP.

02:54.742 --> 02:57.278
- AHH.

02:57.311 --> 02:59.413
WHERE'S THE BATHROOM?
- THERE ISN'T ONE.

02:59.447 --> 03:01.282
[clears throat]

03:01.315 --> 03:02.950
- I FEEL LIKE SOMETHING TO
DRINK--WHERE'S THE KITCHEN?

03:02.983 --> 03:05.353
- SORRY, BUT I HAVE A SINK.

03:05.386 --> 03:07.688
AH.
- AND YOU'LL HAVE A BED,

03:07.721 --> 03:10.858
JUST AS SOON AS WE DRAG THE REST
OF IT UP...

03:10.891 --> 03:13.561
HOW MANY IS IT,
19 FLIGHTS OF STAIRS?

03:13.594 --> 03:14.928
- NO, IT'S ONLY 18.

03:16.997 --> 03:18.566
THANKS AGAIN FOR THE LOAN.

03:18.599 --> 03:20.334
- YEAH, DON'T WORRY ABOUT
RETURNING IT.

03:20.368 --> 03:22.002
- ARE YOU SURE?

03:22.035 --> 03:23.804
- I DOUBT WE'LL
BE NEEDING IT.

03:27.408 --> 03:29.643
- AS SOON AS I DECORATE...

03:29.677 --> 03:30.844
WHAT DO YOU THINK
OF LOUIS COURTURE'S?

03:30.878 --> 03:32.580
- LOVE IT.

03:32.613 --> 03:33.981
- I WILL HAVE YOU AND BEN
OVER FOR DINNER.

03:34.014 --> 03:35.583
- OF COURSE, FIRST
YOU'LL NEED A TABLE.

03:35.616 --> 03:36.850
- AND CHAIRS.

03:36.884 --> 03:38.852
- IS IT WORTH
MENTIONING A STOVE?

03:38.886 --> 03:39.920
- [chuckling]

03:42.656 --> 03:44.792
WELL, IF THERE'S
ANYTHING ELSE I CAN DO...

03:44.825 --> 03:46.460
YOU'VE ALREADY DONE PLENTY.

03:46.494 --> 03:47.795
- YEAH.

03:47.828 --> 03:50.731
I'M SURE BRIAN
WOULD AGREE WITH YOU.

03:50.764 --> 03:52.933
HE BLAMES ME
FOR INFECTING YOU

03:52.966 --> 03:55.336
WITH ALL SORTS
OF HERETICAL IDEAS,

03:55.369 --> 03:57.371
LIKE MARRIAGE AND MONOGAMY

03:57.405 --> 03:59.940
AND A HOUSE AND KIDS.

03:59.973 --> 04:01.742
HE WANTS ME BURNED
AT THE STAKE.

04:01.775 --> 04:03.944
- YOU HAD NOTHING TO DO
WITH IT.

04:03.977 --> 04:05.946
THERE ARE THINGS THAT I HAVE
WANTED FOR A LONG TIME

04:05.979 --> 04:09.517
THAT I COULD NEVER HAVE
IF I STAYED WITH HIM.

04:09.550 --> 04:11.018
I'M JUST SORRY IF IT
RUINED YOUR FRIENDSHIP.

04:11.051 --> 04:13.487
- WELL, HE DID A FINE JOB
OF THAT ON HIS OWN

04:13.521 --> 04:14.955
WITHOUT ANY ASSISTANCE
FROM YOU.

04:16.724 --> 04:18.626
SO...
READY FOR THE BOX SPRING?

04:18.659 --> 04:19.660
[sighs]

04:19.693 --> 04:20.728
[grunts]

04:21.929 --> 04:25.533
- HELLO? HELLO-O?

04:25.566 --> 04:26.900
I KNOW YOU'RE THERE.

04:26.934 --> 04:28.802
I CAN HEAR
YOUR SINUS CONDITION.

04:30.404 --> 04:31.905
- DON'T TELL ME.
ANOTHER ONE?

04:31.939 --> 04:33.040
- FIFTH ONE THIS WEEK.

04:33.073 --> 04:34.508
- ANOTHER WHAT?

04:34.542 --> 04:36.810
- OH...NOTHIN'.

04:36.844 --> 04:39.513
- SWEETHEART, COULD YOU PUT A
LITTLE MORE ROAST BEEF ON THERE

04:39.547 --> 04:41.081
AND, UH,
MAYBE ANOTHER TOMATO?

04:41.114 --> 04:42.816
- YOU KNOW,
CARL'S A DETECTIVE.

04:42.850 --> 04:43.984
MAYBE YOU SHOULD TELL HIM.

04:44.017 --> 04:45.786
- TELL ME WHAT?
- AH, IT'S...

04:45.819 --> 04:47.821
NOT LIKE A CRIME'S BEEN
COMMITTED OR ANYTHING.

04:47.855 --> 04:49.823
IT'S JUST SOMEONE KEEPS CALLING
AND HANGING UP.

04:49.857 --> 04:51.592
- PROBABLY JUST
A WRONG NUMBER.

04:51.625 --> 04:53.961
- OR A STALKER!

04:53.994 --> 04:56.063
WELL, HE IS ON TV.
YOU HEAR ABOUT IT ALL THE TIME.

04:56.096 --> 04:59.066
SOME CRAZED LUNATIC FALLS
MADLY IN LOVE WITH A CELEBRITY

04:59.099 --> 05:00.634
AND WANTS TO MARRY HIM.

05:00.668 --> 05:02.069
OR SLICE HIM UP.

05:02.102 --> 05:04.438
- STALKER...

05:04.472 --> 05:06.106
STALKER?

05:06.139 --> 05:07.741
A STALKER.
OH, MY GOD,

05:07.775 --> 05:09.710
WHAT SHOULD I DO?
HIRE A BODYGUARD?

05:09.743 --> 05:11.078
- WE'LL GET AN ALARM SYSTEM.

05:11.111 --> 05:12.813
- WITH ONE OF THOSE
PANIC BUTTONS

05:12.846 --> 05:14.081
THAT CONNECTS DIRECTLY
TO THE POLICE.

05:14.114 --> 05:15.949
- EXACTLY.
- I AM THE POLICE.

05:15.983 --> 05:17.685
YOU DON'T NEED A BUTTON.

05:17.718 --> 05:19.086
YOU TWO ARE JUMPING
TO CONCLUSIONS.

05:19.119 --> 05:21.889
IF IT IS A STALKER,
HE'S PROBABLY HARMLESS.

05:21.922 --> 05:24.091
HELL, HE'S AFRAID
TO EVEN TALK TO YOU.

05:24.124 --> 05:26.394
JUST KEEP AN EYE OUT.
YOU'LL BE ALL RIGHT.

05:28.729 --> 05:30.964
- AND THAT'S YOUR BEST
PROFESSIONAL ADVICE?

05:30.998 --> 05:32.633
- IT IS.
- YEAH?

05:32.666 --> 05:35.869
WELL, HERE'S MINE.

05:35.903 --> 05:37.738
YOU GET YOURSELF ONE OF THOSE
PEPPER SPRAYS

05:37.771 --> 05:39.440
SO YOU CAN BLAST THE BASTARD.

05:39.473 --> 05:40.974
THEN YOU TAKE ONE OF THOSE
KARATE CLASSES

05:41.008 --> 05:43.411
SO YOU CAN KICK HIM
RIGHT IN THE FUCKIN' BALLS.

05:45.479 --> 05:47.548
HERE, HONEY.
YOU HAVE A SANDWICH.

05:54.488 --> 05:57.725
- HERE YOU GO.
- THANKS.

05:57.758 --> 06:00.594
CHECK OUT THIS LISTING.
- ROOKWOOD VASES ON EBAY?

06:00.628 --> 06:02.463
- CONTRIBUTORS
TO PROPOSITION 14

06:02.496 --> 06:04.998
WHO'VE PUT THEIR MONEY WHERE
THEIR HATEFUL MOUTHS ARE.

06:05.032 --> 06:06.867
- IT'S HARD TO BELIEVE
THERE ARE THAT MANY PEOPLE

06:06.900 --> 06:09.002
WHO DONATE MILLIONS OF DOLLARS
JUST TO PREVENT US

06:09.036 --> 06:11.472
FROM HAVING THE SAME RIGHTS
AS THEY DO.

06:11.505 --> 06:13.807
- I NEED TO GO TO THE CENTER.
I PROMISED I'D VOLUNTEER.

06:13.841 --> 06:15.509
- DON'T WORRY.
I'LL PICK UP GUS AT DAYCARE.

06:15.543 --> 06:16.777
[doorbell rings]

06:22.215 --> 06:23.651
- HEY!

06:23.684 --> 06:25.886
- I'VE COME
FOR MY LITTLE HONEYBUN.

06:25.919 --> 06:27.154
I NEVER THOUGHT
I'D BE TAKING MY...

06:27.187 --> 06:29.089
KID FOR A WORKOUT SO SOON.

06:29.122 --> 06:31.759
- WELL, GYMBOREE'S
NOT EXACTLY RIPT GYM.

06:31.792 --> 06:33.093
I'LL GO GET HER.

06:33.126 --> 06:35.028
PERFECT BLEND OF CREAM
AND HONEY, AS USUAL.

06:35.062 --> 06:36.864
- THANK YOU.
ANY TIME.

06:40.668 --> 06:41.935
- YOU KNOW, IF I DIDN'T
KNOW ANY BETTER,

06:41.969 --> 06:44.037
I'D SAY YOU TWO WERE
BACK TO NORMAL.

06:44.071 --> 06:45.806
- MMM, NOT QUITE.

06:45.839 --> 06:47.908
- UH, IT SURE
LOOKS THAT WAY.

06:47.941 --> 06:51.044
- MEL AND I HAVE DECIDED TO HAVE
AN IN-HOUSE SEPARATION.

06:51.078 --> 06:52.646
- A WHAT?

06:52.680 --> 06:54.648
- IT'S WHAT
OUR THERAPISTS CALL IT.

06:54.682 --> 06:55.916
WE BOTH LIVE IN THE HOUSE.

06:55.949 --> 06:57.451
MEL KEEPS THE SECOND FLOOR,

06:57.485 --> 06:58.919
AND I'M IN THE STUDIO
IN THE ATTIC.

06:58.952 --> 07:00.721
WE SHARE CHORES
AND CHILD CARE,

07:00.754 --> 07:04.792
BUT OTHERWISE, WE LIVE
TOTALLY SEPARATE LIVES.

07:04.825 --> 07:06.527
- I--I CAN'T IMAGINE
BEN AND ME

07:06.560 --> 07:08.662
HAVING THAT KIND
OF AN ARRANGEMENT.

07:08.696 --> 07:09.930
- IT'S NOT AS DIFFICULT
AS IT SOUNDS

07:09.963 --> 07:11.665
ONCE YOU GET THE SYSTEM UP
AND RUNNING.

07:11.699 --> 07:13.967
IN FACT, I'D SAY
IT'S WORKING RATHER WELL.

07:16.103 --> 07:18.972
- HEY! HERE'S OUR
LITTLE OLYMPIC CHAMPION.

07:19.006 --> 07:21.642
YES, YOU ARE.
MWAH!

07:23.176 --> 07:26.079
- HEY, HOW ABOUT
GRABBING SOME LUNCH?

07:26.113 --> 07:28.849
THERE'S A NEW SUSHI BAR
THAT SERVES BLOWFISH.

07:28.882 --> 07:30.951
IT'S EITHER THE MOST DELICIOUS
THING YOU'VE EVER TASTED

07:30.984 --> 07:31.985
OR YOU DIE.

07:32.019 --> 07:34.087
- WELL...

07:34.121 --> 07:36.023
AS TEMPTING AS YOUR OFFER IS,

07:36.056 --> 07:38.125
I'VE ALREADY ORDERED IN.

07:38.158 --> 07:40.227
- OKAY, THEN, UH, HOW ABOUT
AFTER WORK WE GO OUT,

07:40.260 --> 07:42.730
JUST THE TWO OF US, KNOCK BACK
A FEW MANGO MARTINIS?

07:42.763 --> 07:44.464
OF COURSE,
JUST THE MANGO FOR ME.

07:47.735 --> 07:48.902
- HOW MUCH?

07:52.005 --> 07:53.774
- HOW MUCH WHAT?

07:53.807 --> 07:57.110
- HOW MUCH OF A RAISE
ARE YOU GUNNING FOR?

07:57.144 --> 07:58.912
- IS THAT WHAT YOU THINK
I'M AFTER?

07:58.946 --> 08:00.581
- WHY ELSE WOULD YOU BE
THREATENING ME

08:00.614 --> 08:01.915
WITH BLOWFISH AND MANGO
MARTINIS?

08:01.949 --> 08:03.584
- OH, I DON'T KNOW,
I JUST THOUGHT,

08:03.617 --> 08:04.985
CONSIDERING YOU'VE LOST
THE LOVE OF YOUR LIFE

08:05.018 --> 08:07.020
AND YOUR BEST FRIEND,
YOUR SOUL MATE,

08:07.054 --> 08:08.589
THE YIN TO YOUR YANG,
AS IT WERE,

08:08.622 --> 08:10.591
YOU MIGHT WANT SOMEONE
TO SHARE YOUR PAIN WITH.

08:10.624 --> 08:12.860
AND YOU'RE THINKING
THAT SOMEONE MIGHT BE YOU?

08:12.893 --> 08:14.194
HEY...

08:14.227 --> 08:15.863
I'M NOT THE PATHETIC PUTZ,
LOWLY ACCOUNTANT

08:15.896 --> 08:17.297
WHOSE SOLE PURPOSE IN LIFE
IS TO CRUNCH NUMBERS

08:17.330 --> 08:18.732
I ONCE WAS, YOU KNOW.

08:18.766 --> 08:20.000
I'VE BEEN TO HELL AND BACK.

08:20.033 --> 08:21.669
I'VE LOST EVERYTHING,
EVERYONE.

08:21.702 --> 08:23.136
SO I THINK I KNOW WHAT YOU'RE
GOING THROUGH,

08:23.170 --> 08:24.304
EVEN THOUGH
YOU'RE CONCEALING IT, AS ALWAYS,

08:24.337 --> 08:25.773
WITH THE UTMOST SKILL AND
APLOMB.

08:27.074 --> 08:28.508
- THANK YOU, THEODORE.

08:30.077 --> 08:32.880
THE ONLY PAIN
THAT I'M SUFFERING RIGHT NOW

08:32.913 --> 08:36.650
IS FROM THESE
NEW GUCCI LOAFERS.

08:36.684 --> 08:38.619
I KNEW I SHOULD'VE GOTTEN
A SIZE LARGER.

08:38.652 --> 08:41.021
- COME ON, BRI,
YOU CAN'T FOOL ME.

08:41.054 --> 08:43.223
YOU'VE GOT TO FREE YOURSELF
OF THIS BURDEN.

08:43.256 --> 08:45.292
RELEASE IT.

08:45.325 --> 08:46.794
LET IT ALL HANG OUT.

08:53.667 --> 08:55.969
- MY MOTHER
IS A FRIGID BITCH.

08:56.003 --> 08:59.206
MY FATHER
WAS AN ABUSIVE DRUNK.

08:59.239 --> 09:01.642
THEY HAD A HATEFUL MARRIAGE,

09:01.675 --> 09:04.578
WHICH IS PROBABLY
WHY I AM...

09:04.612 --> 09:07.981
UNWILLING OR UNABLE
TO FORM A LONG-TERM,

09:08.015 --> 09:10.918
COMMITTED RELATIONSHIP
OF MY OWN.

09:10.951 --> 09:12.786
THE FACT THAT I DRINK
LIKE A FISH,

09:12.820 --> 09:17.357
ABUSE DRUGS, AND HAVE MORE
OR LESS REDEFINED PROMISCUITY

09:17.390 --> 09:19.760
DOESN'T HELP...MUCH.

09:21.862 --> 09:24.131
AS A RESULT, I'VE LOST
THE TWO PEOPLE IN MY LIFE

09:24.164 --> 09:25.833
THAT MEAN THE MOST TO ME.

09:28.736 --> 09:31.204
- THERE.

09:31.238 --> 09:32.973
DON'T YOU FEEL BETTER?
- NO.

09:34.708 --> 09:35.943
BUT I'M SURE YOU DO.

09:35.976 --> 09:37.711
[knock at door]

09:39.012 --> 09:40.280
NUMBER NINE.

09:41.715 --> 09:44.718
NOW, TED...

09:44.752 --> 09:47.254
IF YOU'LL EXCUSE ME,

09:47.287 --> 09:48.989
MY LUNCH HAS ARRIVED.

09:54.427 --> 09:55.996
- GOOD AFTERNOON,
MR. DEMEERS.

09:56.029 --> 09:57.264
- HELLO, MR. MORGAN.

09:57.297 --> 09:58.899
- MR. LOGAN?

09:58.932 --> 10:00.634
I'M SORRY, MRS. LOGAN.
MY NAME IS JUSTIN.

10:00.668 --> 10:02.035
- HI, I'M CORINNE.
- MELANIE.

10:02.069 --> 10:03.103
I'M CALLING
FROM THE PENNSYLVANIA

10:03.136 --> 10:04.772
ANTI-PROP 14 INITIATIVE.

10:04.805 --> 10:06.139
- ARE YOU FAMILIAR
WITH THE PROPOSED LEGISLATION?

10:06.173 --> 10:07.374
THAT'S RIGHT, SIR.

10:07.407 --> 10:09.142
THE ONE THAT KEEPS GAYS
IN THEIR PLACE.

10:09.176 --> 10:10.878
- CAMPAIGN OF HATE
LED BY REVEREND FOWLER

10:10.911 --> 10:12.746
AND HIS "FAMILY AMERICA"
COALITION.

10:12.780 --> 10:14.748
- THEY WANT THE LEGISLATURE TO
REWRITE THE STATE CONSTITUTION,

10:14.782 --> 10:16.016
LIMITING THE RIGHTS OF GAYS
AND LESBIANS.

10:16.049 --> 10:18.018
- NO, SIR,
I'M NOT A COCKSUCKER.

10:18.051 --> 10:19.252
I'M A LESBIAN.

10:19.286 --> 10:20.988
- IT'S NOT JUST
ABOUT GAY PEOPLE.

10:21.021 --> 10:22.255
IT'S ABOUT EVERY AMERICAN
HAVING THE SAME RIGHTS.

10:22.289 --> 10:23.891
- CAN WE COUNT ON YOU
FOR A DONATION?

10:23.924 --> 10:25.025
- YES, SIR, I'LL BE SURE
TO REMEMBER THAT

10:25.058 --> 10:28.128
AS THEY STUFF ME
INTO THE OVENS!

10:28.161 --> 10:29.730
- [chuckles]
WE'LL SEND YOU A LAWN SIGN.

10:29.763 --> 10:30.764
I'LL PUT A BROCHURE
IN THE MAIL.

10:30.798 --> 10:32.132
THANK YOU FOR YOUR TIME.

10:32.165 --> 10:34.134
- IT'S BEEN A PLEASURE
TALKING TO YOU.

10:34.167 --> 10:36.436
- WHO'D THEY GET THESE LISTS
FROM, THE NAZI PARTY?

10:36.469 --> 10:38.071
- WE'RE GOING OVER THEIR LIST
OF SUPPORTERS,

10:38.105 --> 10:39.873
FIGURING OUT WHICH
BUSINESSES TO TARGET.

10:39.907 --> 10:41.742
- I SAY BOYCOTT THE WHOLE
FUCKING BUNCH OF THEM.

10:41.775 --> 10:44.011
- I SECOND THE MOTION.
- HOLY SHIT.

10:44.044 --> 10:45.746
WOULD YOU LOOK AT THE NAMES
ON HERE?

10:45.779 --> 10:48.415
SOME OF THESE
ARE MAJOR CORPORATIONS.

10:48.448 --> 10:50.050
- THEY MUST
BE RAISING MILLIONS.

10:50.083 --> 10:51.785
- THE HATE SELLS.
WHAT ELSE IS NEW?

10:52.820 --> 10:54.154
- JESUS CHRIST.

10:54.187 --> 10:55.322
- DON'T TELL ME:
HE'S ON THERE TOO?

10:55.355 --> 10:57.124
- WORSE. MY DAD.

11:01.795 --> 11:03.063
[dog barks]

11:06.734 --> 11:08.668
[car alarm wails]

11:10.370 --> 11:11.939
[banging]

11:13.106 --> 11:15.208
- [sighs]
NOW, EM,

11:15.242 --> 11:17.477
DON'T BE SUCH
A SCAREDY-QUEEN.

11:17.510 --> 11:19.179
NO ONE'S STALKING YOU.

11:19.212 --> 11:21.782
WHY WOULD ANYBODY
STALK YOU?

11:21.815 --> 11:23.483
JUST BECAUSE YOU'RE
ON CHANNEL FIVE NEWS

11:23.516 --> 11:26.353
AND EVERYONE ADORES
THE QUEER GUY AND...

11:26.386 --> 11:27.788
OF COURSE,
THERE IS THE UNDENIABLE FACT

11:27.821 --> 11:29.957
THAT YOU DO HAVE
AN AWESOME ASS. I...

11:29.990 --> 11:31.324
AAH! OH, PLEASE!

11:31.358 --> 11:33.093
PLEASE, YOU CAN HAVE
ANYTHING YOU WANT!

11:33.126 --> 11:34.828
TAKE MY BAG! I-I'LL GIVE YOU
AN AUTOGRAPHED PICTURE!

11:34.862 --> 11:36.463
- EMMETT!

11:36.496 --> 11:38.365
- OH, MY GOD.

11:38.398 --> 11:39.767
DREW!

11:41.368 --> 11:43.136
WHAT'S UP?

11:43.170 --> 11:46.373
- EVERY TIME I'D GET UP
THE NERVE TO PHONE YOU,

11:46.406 --> 11:49.509
I'D HANG UP, AFRAID SOMEBODY
MIGHT BE TAPPING MY LINE.

11:49.542 --> 11:52.079
- YOU'RE "THE BREATHER"?

11:52.112 --> 11:55.248
YOU SHOULD REALLY DO SOMETHING
ABOUT THOSE SINUSES.

11:55.282 --> 11:57.785
- [chuckles] I KNOW.
IT'S MY ALLERGIES.

11:59.787 --> 12:01.889
- SO OTHER THAN THE RAGWEED,

12:01.922 --> 12:04.858
HOW YOU BEEN?

12:04.892 --> 12:06.426
- NOT SO GOOD.

12:06.459 --> 12:07.895
- YOU PLAYED
IN THE CHAMPIONSHIP.

12:09.129 --> 12:10.764
- I WAS IN WOODY'S AND...

12:10.798 --> 12:12.265
IT JUST HAPPENED TO BE ON,

12:12.299 --> 12:15.235
AND I JUST HAPPENED TO CATCH
YOUR WINNING TOUCHDOWN.

12:15.268 --> 12:17.137
- [chuckles]

12:17.170 --> 12:20.173
- THEN I JUST HAPPENED TO READ
ABOUT YOUR WEDDING TO SIERRA.

12:20.207 --> 12:23.977
- CONGRATULATIONS.
- THANKS.

12:24.011 --> 12:27.014
WE'RE GETTING A DIVORCE.

12:27.047 --> 12:28.916
THAT'S WHY I WAS TRYING
TO CALL YOU.

12:32.319 --> 12:34.855
I NEED SOMEONE
I CAN TALK TO, EMMETT.

12:34.888 --> 12:36.156
