THE PHONE ALL WEEK FOR NOTHING.

16:13.706 --> 16:15.042
[bumps into chair]

16:21.781 --> 16:22.682
- BEN?

16:24.551 --> 16:25.518
BEN?

16:26.553 --> 16:27.654
- I'M IN HERE.

16:30.790 --> 16:34.361
- YOU'RE SMOKING IN THE HOUSE
WITHOUT EVEN A WINDOW OPEN?

16:34.394 --> 16:35.595
