16:59.752 --> 17:02.189
- WELL, UNLIKE YOU,
I STILL HAVE A LITTLE FAITH.

17:02.222 --> 17:03.790
- FAITH, DENIAL,

17:03.823 --> 17:05.325
EVERYONE MAKES
THEIR OWN CHOICES.

17:05.358 --> 17:10.330
