18:16.363 --> 18:18.631
- HMM.

18:18.665 --> 18:21.501
- AH. AND THERE'S
MY NUMBER NINE NOW.

18:21.534 --> 18:26.273
[muffled house music]

18:26.306 --> 18:28.208
- DO YOU REALIZE
