I'D NEVER SEE HIM AGAIN.

20:09.676 --> 20:12.479
- WELL, MAYBE YOU WERE JUST
FEELING SORRY FOR HIM, POOR GUY.

20:12.512 --> 20:14.614
- I TOLD HIM HOW HE COULD
PUT A STOP TO THE WHOLE THING.

20:14.647 --> 20:16.616
