TO EVERYONE

20:22.922 --> 20:24.624
FROM THE MOMENT I POPPED OUT
OF MY MAMA

20:24.657 --> 20:26.593
THAT I WAS THE NEW
QUEEN OF HAZELHURST.

20:26.626 --> 20:28.361
