ELIZABETH.

20:28.395 --> 20:29.729
- YOU WERE LUCKY.

20:29.762 --> 20:31.731
- THAT THEY NAMED ME EMMETT?

20:31.764 --> 20:33.500
- THAT IT WAS OBVIOUS.

20:33.533 --> 20:35.635
