21:03.563 --> 21:05.932
AND IN MY INEBRIATED STATE
I CONFESSED TO HIM

21:05.965 --> 21:07.367
THAT I KIND OF
SORT OF TOTALLY HAD

21:07.400 --> 21:09.369
