CRUSH ON HIM.

21:09.402 --> 21:10.903
- AND HE SAID, "ME TOO!"

21:10.937 --> 21:13.406
AND YOU FELL
INTO EACH OTHERS' ARMS.

21:15.107 --> 21:16.809
- HE PUNCHED ME IN THE NOSE,

21:16.843 --> 21:19.579
THEN TOLD EVERYBODY
IN THE HOUSE I WAS A FAG.

21:19.612 --> 21:23.082
AFTER THAT,
I WAS CEREMONIOUSLY UN-ZAPPED.

21:23.115 --> 21:25.452
- I NEVER KNEW, TEDDY.

21:25.485 --> 21:27.086
- I MEAN, IT WAS
HARD ENOUGH FOR ME,

21:27.119 --> 21:29.556
