21:46.138 --> 21:47.574
- JOHNNY WALKER.

21:49.609 --> 21:51.878
AND, UH, SOME EXTRA NUTS.

21:55.114 --> 21:57.517
WHY...ALEX?

21:59.051 --> 22:01.454
[grunting]

22:05.458 --> 22:07.994
