OF CAP'N CRUNCH.

22:30.149 --> 22:33.486
"KEEP YOUR FUCKIN' HANDS OFF!
HUNTER."

22:33.520 --> 22:35.054
- SOUNDS LIKE A NOVOTNY.

22:40.493 --> 22:42.061
