22:42.094 --> 22:45.598
- NOT A FUCKING WORD.
CAN YOU BELIEVE THAT?

22:45.632 --> 22:46.899
THAT UNGRATEFUL
LITTLE PRICK.

22:46.933 --> 22:48.067
AFTER ALL WE DID FOR HIM,

22:48.100 --> 22:50.002
