TO SURVIVE.

23:43.089 --> 23:45.725
AND THAT HE KNOWS
YOU'RE STILL HERE FOR HIM,

23:45.758 --> 23:47.126
IN CASE SOMEDAY
HE CHANGES HIS MIND

23:47.159 --> 23:50.530
