GET THAT OUT OF YOUR HEADS.

23:54.567 --> 23:57.236
[glass clinking]

23:57.269 --> 23:59.706
- SURE, I'M INTO THAT.
NO PROBLEM.

23:59.739 --> 24:00.940
50 BUCKS.

24:00.973 --> 24:03.476
[indistinct chatter]

24:03.510 --> 24:06.746
