25:54.821 --> 25:56.122
- IT'S NOT JUST THE ONIONS.

25:56.155 --> 25:57.990
- I KNOW.

25:58.024 --> 26:00.326
- IT'S--IT'S BEEN
SO LONG SINCE I--

26:00.359 --> 26:02.695
