26:02.729 --> 26:04.230
SOME OTHER TIME.

26:04.263 --> 26:05.231
- [clears throat]

26:15.174 --> 26:16.609
[door opens]

26:16.643 --> 26:17.710
- [gasps]
OH.

26:19.245 --> 26:21.313
I'M SORRY.

26:23.983 --> 26:25.985
THE TRASH COMES
TOMORROW AND...

26:27.319 --> 26:29.622
- LINZ, THIS IS CORINNE.

26:29.656 --> 26:30.623
- HEY.

26:30.657 --> 26:31.791
- HI.

26:33.660 --> 26:34.961
- WE VOLUNTEER

26:34.994 --> 26:36.328
AT THE CENTER TOGETHER.

26:38.430 --> 26:39.966
- I JUST REMEMBERED,

26:39.999 --> 26:42.702
I FORGOT THE TRASH
FROM UPSTAIRS.

26:42.735 --> 26:44.036
SO I'LL JUST...

26:44.070 --> 26:45.738
GO UP AND COLLECT IT.

26:47.006 --> 26:49.008
THE TRASH FROM UPSTAIRS.

26:52.211 --> 26:54.013
[door closes]

26:58.017 --> 26:59.051
- [clears throat]

27:01.087 --> 27:02.722
- PEACH...

27:02.755 --> 27:04.056
A LA MODE.

27:04.090 --> 27:05.758
- OH. NO, THANKS.

27:07.226 --> 27:08.895
SHAME TO LET IT MELT.

27:08.928 --> 27:11.130
SO YOU STILL GETTING CALLS
FROM "THE BREATHER"?

27:11.163 --> 27:13.399
- I HAVE A FEELING
THOSE HAVE STOPPED FOR GOOD.

27:13.432 --> 27:15.134
- THAT'S A RELIEF.

27:15.167 --> 27:17.303
- ACTUALLY,
I KIND OF MISS 'EM.

27:20.106 --> 27:23.009
- JUICE. COFFEE.

27:23.042 --> 27:24.310
THREE EGG WHITES, SCRAMBLED.

27:24.343 --> 27:25.812
- IT'S A LITTLE LATE
FOR BREAKFAST.

27:25.845 --> 27:27.313
- NOT IF YOU'VE BEEN UP
ALL NIGHT.

27:27.346 --> 27:29.882
- YOU KNOW, A MAN YOUR AGE

27:29.916 --> 27:31.083
SHOULD TAKE BETTER CARE
OF HIMSELF.

27:31.117 --> 27:32.952
YOU COULD DIE OF A STROKE.

27:32.985 --> 27:34.787
- I'M COUNTING ON YOU
TO GET TO ME FIRST.

27:34.821 --> 27:37.156
- UH-HUH.

27:37.189 --> 27:38.357
- SO WHERE WERE YOU?

27:38.390 --> 27:40.359
TOOL SHED? SLAMMER?
THE PISS HOLE?

27:40.392 --> 27:41.894
- PUERTO VALLARTA.

27:41.928 --> 27:44.897
- MM, MUST BE A NEW ONE.
WHERE IS IT?

27:44.931 --> 27:46.365
- MEXICO.

27:46.398 --> 27:47.834
YOU WENT TO...

27:47.867 --> 27:49.769
- AND BACK
IN LESS THAN 24 HOURS.

27:49.802 --> 27:51.904
- WELL, THAT WAS A QUICKIE.

27:51.938 --> 27:53.439
- IN MORE WAYS THAN ONE.

27:53.472 --> 27:56.242
I HAD A PRESSING PIECE OF
BUSINESS TO ATTEND TO.

27:56.275 --> 27:57.777
- AND DID YOU
TAKE CARE OF IT?

27:57.810 --> 27:59.445
- ONCE, AT CRUISING ALTITUDE,

27:59.478 --> 28:01.981
AND ONCE WHILE WE WERE
MAKING OUR APPROACH.

28:03.382 --> 28:05.852
- COFFEE, JUICE--
EGGS'LL BE READY

28:05.885 --> 28:07.820
SOON AS THE HENS
FINISH LAYING 'EM.

28:09.221 --> 28:10.923
- YOU THINK HE'S A TOP?

28:10.957 --> 28:12.792
- SOME OF THOSE HUNKS,
WHEN YOU GET THEM IN BED,

28:12.825 --> 28:14.927
TURN OUT TO BE
THE BIGGEST BOTTOMS.

28:14.961 --> 28:17.329
- I'D DO HIM EITHER WAY.

28:17.363 --> 28:19.365
- AND WHO MIGHT THAT BE?

28:19.398 --> 28:21.367
- THE QUEEN WHO JUST
GOT OUTED.

28:29.441 --> 28:31.277
- EXCUSE ME, SIR,
YOU MIGHT WANT TO READ THIS

28:31.310 --> 28:33.212
BEFORE YOU SHOP
AT TAYLOR ELECTRONICS.

28:33.245 --> 28:34.814
- DO YOU KNOW THAT THE OWNER
OF THIS STORE

28:34.847 --> 28:36.282
IS A HATE-MONGERING BIGOT

28:36.315 --> 28:38.484
WHO WANTS TO DENY HONEST
CITIZENS THEIR RIGHTS?

28:38.517 --> 28:42.054
- DON'T SUPPORT BUSINESSES THAT
DON'T SUPPORT ALL AMERICANS!

28:44.456 --> 28:46.358
- EXCUSE ME, FOLKS,

28:46.392 --> 28:48.494
BUT YOU'RE TRESPASSING
ON PRIVATE PROPERTY.

28:48.527 --> 28:51.130
- DO YOU WANT TO DENY US
A FEW MORE LIBERTIES?

28:51.163 --> 28:52.398
- MA'AM, IF YOU DON'T LEAVE,

28:52.431 --> 28:53.900
WE'LL BE FORCED
TO MAKE YOU LEAVE.

28:53.933 --> 28:56.302
- OH, YEAH?
WELL, MY HUSBAND...

28:56.335 --> 28:59.171
'CEPT I'M NOT MARRIED 'CAUSE MY
GAY SON HERE CAN'T GET MARRIED,

28:59.205 --> 29:01.307
HAPPENS TO BE DETECTIVE
CARL HORVATH.

29:01.340 --> 29:03.242
EVER HEARD OF HIM?
- YES, MA'AM.

29:03.275 --> 29:05.111
I'VE HEARD OF YOU TOO.

29:05.144 --> 29:07.413
- IT'S NO PROBLEM, OFFICER.
COME ON, MOM.

29:07.446 --> 29:08.547
- YEAH, LET'S MOVE ACROSS
THE STREET, GUYS.

29:08.580 --> 29:09.916
WE CAN STILL
MAKE OUR POINT

29:09.949 --> 29:11.383
WITHOUT GETTING
INTO TROUBLE.

29:11.417 --> 29:13.786
- WELL, WE'LL JUST
YELL TWICE AS LOUD!

29:13.820 --> 29:15.221
all: YEAH!

29:16.355 --> 29:17.790
- YOU TOO, SON.

29:17.824 --> 29:20.526
- I'M NOT YOUR SON.
I'M HIS.

29:20.559 --> 29:22.161
AND I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

29:22.194 --> 29:23.529
- WHATEVER ISSUES YOU HAVE
WITH YOUR FATHER,

29:23.562 --> 29:25.164
YOU SHOULD SETTLE THEM
OFF THE STREET.

29:25.197 --> 29:27.166
- I ALREADY TRIED THAT.

29:28.901 --> 29:30.536
I'M STANDING IN FRONT
OF YOUR DOOR, DAD,

29:30.569 --> 29:32.304
IN FRONT OF YOUR FACE.

29:32.338 --> 29:34.040
NOW YOU CAN CALL IN
YOUR TROOPS,

29:34.073 --> 29:35.341
BUT I'M NOT GOING
TO DISAPPEAR.

29:35.374 --> 29:38.010
SO WHAT ARE YOU
GOING TO DO, HMM?

29:38.044 --> 29:40.446
COME ON, DAD, WHY DON'T YOU SHOW
US YOUR GREAT FAMILY VALUES

29:40.479 --> 29:42.114
AND HAVE THEM
ARREST YOUR SON.

29:44.216 --> 29:45.184
- SIR?

29:48.187 --> 29:49.455
- GO ON.

29:49.488 --> 29:51.057
- YOU SURE YOU WANT
TO DO THAT, SIR?

29:51.090 --> 29:53.325
- I TOLD YOU TO GET HIM
OUT OF HERE.

29:56.395 --> 29:58.064
- YOU ARE HEREBY ARRESTED

29:58.097 --> 30:00.566
FOR UNLAWFULLY TRESPASSING
ON PRIVATE PROPERTY.

30:00.599 --> 30:02.368
ANYTHING YOU SAY MAY
AND WILL BE USED AGAINST YOU

30:02.401 --> 30:03.903
IN A COURT OF LAW.

30:03.936 --> 30:05.304
YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
TO AN ATTORNEY...

30:05.337 --> 30:07.206
[protestors chanting]

30:10.609 --> 30:12.478
- MEET MY NUMBER TEN.

30:12.511 --> 30:14.113
- I ALREADY HAVE.

30:14.146 --> 30:15.581
HE WAS MY NUMBER...

30:15.614 --> 30:17.449
FIVE, I BELIEVE.

30:17.483 --> 30:19.451
ANYWAY, YOU NEEDN'T BOTHER.

30:19.485 --> 30:20.920
I ALREADY WON.

30:20.953 --> 30:24.223
- [scoffs]
WELL, THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE.

30:24.256 --> 30:25.958
GUY'S IN PUERTO VALLARTA.

30:27.894 --> 30:32.932
WE BOTH HAD A LOVELY FLIGHT.

30:32.965 --> 30:35.968
ALTHOUGH THERE WAS A LITTLE
TURBULENCE IN THE TOILET.

30:37.636 --> 30:40.606
GAME, SET AND MATCH,
SPORT.

30:40.639 --> 30:43.009
THE WINNER,
AND STILL CHAMPION,

30:43.042 --> 30:46.412
IS YOURS TRULY.

30:46.445 --> 30:49.515
- SO I GUESS YOU'LL BE WANTING
TO COLLECT YOUR TROPHY.

30:49.548 --> 30:51.050
- YOU BET YOUR ASS.

30:53.119 --> 30:54.853
SO YOU'D BETTER POLISH IT UP.

30:59.125 --> 31:01.093
- HE SAID HE'D GO
TO THE PRESS,

31:01.127 --> 31:03.963
THAT IF I DIDN'T PAY HIM,
THE TABLOIDS WOULD.

31:03.996 --> 31:05.531
SO I TOLD HIM
TO GO FUCK HIMSELF,

31:05.564 --> 31:07.399
I WASN'T GOING TO GIVE HIM
ANOTHER CENT.

31:07.433 --> 31:10.002
NOW THE DAMN PAPARAZZIS
SURROUNDED MY HOUSE.

31:10.036 --> 31:11.904
I CAN'T EVEN GO HOME.

31:11.938 --> 31:15.274
I FEEL LIKE A FUGITIVE,
A...CRIMINAL!

31:15.307 --> 31:17.443
- YEAH, THAT'S WHY I CALLED,

31:17.476 --> 31:19.145
TO LET YOU KNOW
YOU HAVE A FRIEND.

31:21.480 --> 31:22.681
- I'VE ALREADY
CALLED MY LAWYERS.

31:22.714 --> 31:24.183
I'M GOING TO FILE
A LAWSUIT.

31:24.216 --> 31:26.318
SUE 'EM FOR 30 MILLION.

31:26.352 --> 31:28.587
- WHAT ABOUT THE PHOTOGRAPHS?
THEY'RE REAL.

31:28.620 --> 31:31.057
- I'LL DENY IT.

31:31.090 --> 31:34.126
I'LL SAY THEY WERE PHOTOSHOPPED,
THE WORK OF A BLACKMAILER.

31:34.160 --> 31:35.461
THEY THINK THEY CAN
MESS WITH ME,

31:35.494 --> 31:37.463
THEY'VE GOT
ANOTHER THING COMING.

31:37.496 --> 31:40.399
THIS TIME, THEY FUCKED
WITH THE WRONG GUY!

31:40.432 --> 31:42.068
- WHAT ABOUT THE NEXT TIME?

31:42.101 --> 31:44.170
- THERE ISN'T GOING TO BE
A NEXT TIME.

31:44.203 --> 31:46.172
- OH, YOU PLANNING
ON GIVING UP SEX?

31:46.205 --> 31:47.940
- WHO SAID THAT?

31:47.974 --> 31:49.575
THERE'RE PLENTY OF WOMEN.

31:49.608 --> 31:51.210
- MAYBE SO, BUT...

31:51.243 --> 31:52.544
WHEN'S THE LAST TIME
YOU HAD SEX WITH A WOMAN

31:52.578 --> 31:54.180
THAT YOU DIDN'T THINK
ABOUT A MAN?

31:58.217 --> 32:01.187
IT'S WHO YOU ARE, BABY.

32:01.220 --> 32:03.455
YOU CAN'T FIGHT IT.

32:03.489 --> 32:05.958
SOONER OR LATER, THERE'RE
GOING TO BE OTHER GUYS.

32:05.992 --> 32:08.294
AND EACH TIME THERE ARE,
YOU'LL BE SCARED SHITLESS

32:08.327 --> 32:10.963
WONDERING,
"DID HE RECOGNIZE ME?

32:10.997 --> 32:13.699
IS HE GOING TO BLACKMAIL ME?
IS HE GOING TO THE TABLOIDS?"

32:13.732 --> 32:16.935
I MEAN, IS THAT HOW YOU WANT
TO SPEND THE REST OF YOUR LIFE?

32:23.409 --> 32:25.511
- THANKS FOR BAILING ME OUT.

32:25.544 --> 32:27.980
- WHEN I TAUGHT YOU TO SAY
"PLEASE" AND "THANK YOU,"

32:28.014 --> 32:31.050
I NEVER QUITE EXPECTED
TO HEAR IT USED THAT WAY.

32:31.083 --> 32:32.618
- YOU TOO, BEN.
- ANYTIME.

32:32.651 --> 32:34.186
ACTUALLY, I TAKE THAT BACK.

32:34.220 --> 32:35.521
LET'S HOPE
IT'S THE LAST TIME.

32:35.554 --> 32:37.389
- YOU CAN DAMN WELL
BE SURE OF THAT.

32:37.423 --> 32:39.725
I'M GOING TO HAVE A FEW WORDS
WITH YOUR FATHER,

32:39.758 --> 32:42.128
STARTING WITH, "YOU SICK
SON OF A BITCH!"

32:42.161 --> 32:44.530
- I WOULDN'T WASTE YOUR BREATH.
HE'S NOT WORTH IT.

32:44.563 --> 32:46.198
- I CAN'T BELIEVE A FATHER
WOULD ACTUALLY

32:46.232 --> 32:48.067
HAVE HIS OWN SON ARRESTED.

32:48.100 --> 32:49.668
- AND I DON'T BELIEVE YOU'VE
EVER HAD THE DISPLEASURE

32:49.701 --> 32:51.770
OF MEETING MY EX-HUSBAND.

32:51.803 --> 32:53.672
- I USED TO THINK IN TIME,
HE WOULD COME AROUND.

32:53.705 --> 32:56.442
BUT NOW I THINK THAT HE WOULD
RATHER SEE ME DEAD THAN GAY.

32:58.510 --> 33:01.247
- YOUR DAD DOESN'T KNOW
HOW LUCKY HE IS TO HAVE A SON.

33:03.549 --> 33:05.251
WHY DON'T I GO GET THE CAR?

33:05.284 --> 33:06.652
- YEAH. THANKS, BEN.

33:11.257 --> 33:13.359
I JUST WANT YOU TO KNOW THAT,
EVEN THOUGH YOUR FATHER

33:13.392 --> 33:17.129
MAY NO LONGER CONSIDER
YOU HIS SON,

33:17.163 --> 33:19.165
YOU WILL ALWAYS BE MINE.

33:19.198 --> 33:20.699
- THANKS.

33:20.732 --> 33:23.435
I'M JUST SORRY
I FUCKED THINGS UP.

33:23.469 --> 33:25.304
- FUCKED WHAT UP?

33:25.337 --> 33:27.506
- WELL, DAD SAYS IT'S ON ACCOUNT
OF ME, THAT...

33:27.539 --> 33:31.243
THAT I'M THE ONE THAT DESTROYED
YOUR MARRIAGE.

33:31.277 --> 33:33.579
- HONEY, YOU DON'T
REALLY BELIEVE THAT?

33:33.612 --> 33:35.181
- MM.

33:35.214 --> 33:37.683
- WELL, IT'S NOT TRUE.

33:37.716 --> 33:39.251
WE WERE HAVING PROBLEMS

33:39.285 --> 33:41.820
LONG BEFORE YOU
TOLD US YOU'RE GAY.

33:41.853 --> 33:44.056
SO, IF HE WANTS TO LIE
TO HIMSELF

33:44.090 --> 33:46.058
AND BLAME YOU, LET HIM.

33:46.092 --> 33:50.196
DON'T YOU DARE BLAME YOURSELF.

33:50.229 --> 33:51.697
HMM?
- YEAH.

33:56.302 --> 33:59.138
- IT WAS SO AWFUL SEEING MEL
KISSING THAT WOMAN,

33:59.171 --> 34:01.473
WHILE I JUST STOOD THERE
HOLDING THE GARBAGE.

34:01.507 --> 34:03.442
- HMM, I THINK IT'S SHOCKING.

34:03.475 --> 34:05.211
- ISN'T IT?

34:05.244 --> 34:08.314
- I MEAN, THAT SOMEONE WOULD
WANT TO KISS MEL.

34:08.347 --> 34:09.681
- OW!

34:09.715 --> 34:11.617
FUCK!

34:11.650 --> 34:13.852
- YOU DESERVED THAT.

34:13.885 --> 34:15.287
YOU WANT ME TO RUB
THE BOO-BOO

34:15.321 --> 34:16.622
AND MAKE IT BETTER?

34:16.655 --> 34:19.225
- YOU LEAVE MY BOO-BOO ALONE.

34:19.258 --> 34:21.093
CHRIST.

34:21.127 --> 34:22.861
YOU CAN BARELY TURN AROUND
IN HERE.

34:22.894 --> 34:24.630
- WELL, WHERE ELSE AM I
SUPPOSED TO GO?

34:24.663 --> 34:26.498
SLEEP IN THE KITCHEN
OR ON THE FRONT PORCH?

34:26.532 --> 34:29.301
- THIS WHOLE IN-HOUSE SEPARATION
IS FOR SHIT.

34:29.335 --> 34:31.870
- WE NEED TO DO IT
FOR FINANCIAL REASONS.

34:31.903 --> 34:33.605
- AT THE EXPENSE
OF YOUR EMOTIONAL REASON?

34:34.806 --> 34:35.874
AND WHAT'S NEXT?

34:35.907 --> 34:37.176
YOU COME IN ON THEM FUCKING?

34:37.209 --> 34:38.477
- DON'T SAY THAT.

34:38.510 --> 34:39.578
- CAN'T FACE IT?

34:39.611 --> 34:41.780
- NO, I CAN'T FACE IT.

34:46.418 --> 34:49.721
I GUESS WHEN I MOVED BACK
INTO THIS HOUSE, I...

34:49.755 --> 34:54.493
THOUGHT, DESPITE WHAT I KNEW,
DESPITE THE RULES, THAT...

34:54.526 --> 34:56.328
SOMEHOW, MEL AND I WOULD...

34:56.362 --> 34:58.096
- WOULD GET BACK TOGETHER.

35:00.232 --> 35:03.369
YOU DYKES JUST CAN'T
LET GO, CAN YOU?

35:03.402 --> 35:06.338
JUST CAN'T GET IT THROUGH
YOUR LESBIANIC BRAINS

35:06.372 --> 35:09.475
THAT YOU HAVE TO STOP CLINGING
TO YOUR PAST AND MOVE ON.

35:09.508 --> 35:11.210
- MOVE ON?

35:11.243 --> 35:14.146
THAT'S A GOOD ONE,
COMING FROM YOU.

35:14.180 --> 35:15.914
CARRYING ON LIKE
AN OVER-SEXED ADOLESCENT,

35:15.947 --> 35:18.417
THAT "FUCK-OFF" OF YOURS.

35:20.252 --> 35:21.687
YES, I KNOW ALL ABOUT IT.

35:21.720 --> 35:23.755
EVERYONE KNOWS
ALL ABOUT IT.

35:23.789 --> 35:25.624
A CHILDISH COMPETITION
BETWEEN YOU

35:25.657 --> 35:27.493
AND THIS YEAR'S
YOUNG HOT STUD.

35:27.526 --> 35:29.528
NOT ONLY IS IT LUDICROUS,

35:29.561 --> 35:31.530
IT'S HUMILIATING.

35:33.532 --> 35:35.401
WELL, I HOPE YOU WIN.

35:35.434 --> 35:39.438
EVEN THOUGH YOU'VE ALREADY LOST
SOMETHING FAR MORE VALUABLE.

35:42.341 --> 35:45.244
SO DON'T YOU TELL ME ABOUT
CLINGING ON TO MY PAST

35:45.277 --> 35:47.579
UNTIL YOU'RE WILLING
TO LET GO OF YOURS.

35:57.323 --> 35:58.957
- [on TV] STOP RIGHT THERE!

35:58.990 --> 36:02.361
- I'M A POLICE OFFICER.
DETECTIVE ELAINE BENDER, METRO.

36:02.394 --> 36:03.795
HEY. HEY!

36:03.829 --> 36:06.465
- YOU KNOW, I SOLVE CRIMES
FOR A LIVING.

36:06.498 --> 36:08.800
AND I CAN TELL YOU, IT DOESN'T
HAPPEN IN 60 MINUTES

36:08.834 --> 36:11.737
WITH THE HELP OF A PARTNER
WHO LOOKS LIKE A RUNWAY MODEL.

36:11.770 --> 36:13.939
- THAT'S WHY THERE'S
NO CSI: PITTSBURGH.

36:13.972 --> 36:16.208
- [chuckles]
[doorbell rings]

36:16.242 --> 36:17.809
- SWEETHEART,
WOULD YOU GET THAT?

36:17.843 --> 36:24.850
THE RUNWAY MODEL'S
ABOUT TO NAIL THE KILLER.

36:24.883 --> 36:26.952
- OH, MY GOD!
DREW BOYD.

36:26.985 --> 36:28.754
UH, WE MET YOU LAST YEAR
AT THE GAME.

36:28.787 --> 36:30.356
- I REMEMBER.

36:30.389 --> 36:31.990
YOU WERE WITH THIS LOUD WOMAN
WITH RED HAIR.

36:32.023 --> 36:34.693
- THAT WOULD BE ME.

36:34.726 --> 36:36.295
- UH, IS--
IS EMMETT HERE?

36:36.328 --> 36:37.829
- HONEY, IS EMMETT HERE?

36:37.863 --> 36:40.366
- EMMETT!

36:40.399 --> 36:41.500
- COME IN, PLEASE.
- THANK YOU.

36:44.670 --> 36:47.306
- LOOK, I-I JUST
WANT YOU TO KNOW,

36:47.339 --> 36:49.908
I DON'T CARE WHAT YOU DO IN BED
OR WHO YOU DO IT WITH.

36:49.941 --> 36:52.878
YOU'RE STILL ONE HELL
OF A BALL PLAYER.

36:52.911 --> 36:56.882
- YOU HAVE NO IDEA HOW SORRY
I AM YOU HAD TO SAY THAT.

36:56.915 --> 36:58.617
BUT HOW GLAD I AM YOU DID.

36:59.685 --> 37:00.986
- DEB...

37:01.019 --> 37:02.521
DID YOU CALL?

37:16.835 --> 37:19.271
- WANT SOME?
- NO, THANKS.

37:19.305 --> 37:21.039
- SURE?
THERE'S ENOUGH FOR TWO.

37:21.072 --> 37:22.908
- WE EACH MAKE OUR OWN DINNER.
ISN'T THAT WHAT WE AGREED ON?

37:27.846 --> 37:29.948
- LINZ, I'M SO SORRY...

37:29.981 --> 37:32.017
FOR THAT KISS WITH CORINNE.

37:32.050 --> 37:33.819
THAT YOU HAD TO SEE IT,
THAT WE DID IT

37:33.852 --> 37:35.487
RIGHT IN FRONT OF YOU.

37:35.521 --> 37:37.823
- PLEASE, DON'T GIVE IT
ANOTHER THOUGHT. REALLY.

37:37.856 --> 37:41.026
IN FACT, I'M THE ONE WHO SHOULD
APOLOGIZE TO YOU,

37:41.059 --> 37:42.761
FOR INTRUDING.

37:42.794 --> 37:45.564
- IT'S PRETTY MESSY, HUH?
- YEAH, I'LL SAY.

37:45.597 --> 37:48.534
- MM, I THINK WE SHOULD DO
SOMETHING ABOUT THIS.

37:50.669 --> 37:52.304
I THINK WE SHOULD
MAKE IT A RULE

37:52.338 --> 37:53.439
THAT IF WE'RE
DATING SOMEONE--

37:53.472 --> 37:55.307
- ARE YOU DATING HER?

37:57.476 --> 37:58.510
- NO.

37:58.544 --> 37:59.511
NOT REALLY.

37:59.545 --> 38:00.712
UH, I DON'T THINK SO.

38:00.746 --> 38:01.947
- BUT YOU'RE SEEING HER.

38:01.980 --> 38:03.582
- WELL, I GUESS...

38:03.615 --> 38:05.551
I DON'T KNOW.
WELL, ANYWAY, I WAS SAYING--

38:05.584 --> 38:07.586
- I'M SORRY. FORGIVE ME,
I INTERRUPTED YOU.

38:07.619 --> 38:09.054
- NO, NO, NO. IT'S OKAY.
- GO ON.

38:09.087 --> 38:10.989
- I WAS JUST SAYING
THAT IF THERE'S ANYONE

38:11.022 --> 38:12.791
EITHER ONE OF US
HAS AN INTEREST IN,

38:12.824 --> 38:14.526
THAT WE SHOULD
MAKE IT A RULE

38:14.560 --> 38:15.827
THAT WE DON'T BRING THAT PERSON
HOME, TO THE HOUSE.

38:15.861 --> 38:17.329
- I AGREE.

38:17.363 --> 38:18.864
- GOOD.

38:18.897 --> 38:20.932
- SEE? WE CAN WORK
THESE THINGS OUT.

38:20.966 --> 38:23.869
- THANK GOD,
WE'RE STILL MATURE ADULTS

